// 1. Reviewing the database merge policy

.show database ['drone-telemetry'] policy merge 

// 2. Altering tags on all extents of a table

.alter extent tags ('Drone telemetry data. ') <| .show table ['fleet data'] extents

// 3. Adding tags on all extents of a table

.alter-merge extent tags ('Data source: telemetry data lake.') <| .show table ['fleet data'] extents


// 3. Reviewing extent tags

.show table ['fleet data'] extents
| project ExtentId, Tags
